FSync no
MaxMessages 200
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User azuwis@gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
AuthMechs LOGIN
PassCmd "pass show email/azuwis@gmail.com"

IMAPStore gmail
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Maildir/gmail/
Inbox ~/Maildir/gmail/inbox/

Channel gmail-inbox
Master :gmail:
Slave :gmail-local:

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:sent
MaxMessages 100

Channel gmail-drafts
Master :gmail:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :gmail-local:drafts
MaxMessages 100

# Channel gmail-test
# Master :gmail:
# Slave :gmail-local:
# Patterns *

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-drafts
